Title: Return to Halloweentown
Writer: Max Enscoe (teleplay), Annie DeYoung (teleplay), Juliet Giglio (teleplay), Keith Giglio (teleplay), Paul Bernbaum (characters)
Actors: Sara Paxton, Judith Hoag, Lucas Grabeel, Joey Zimmerman
Plot: Marnie and Dylan are going to follow their dreams to go to college, at Halloweentown University, which is also known as Witch University.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Primetime Emmy. Another 2 nominations.
